WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:02.750 --> 00:00:10.750
Earth. a cradle for unimaginable
beauty and staggering wonder.

2
00:00:10.880 --> 00:00:17.890
Incomprehensible. overwhelming...
this planet mocks our feeble power...

3
00:00:17.970 --> 00:00:19.810
