6
00:00:30.360 --> 00:00:33.700
Behold the defiler.

7
00:00:33.780 --> 00:00:39.496
His character is vile.
base. and depraved.

8
00:00:39.580 --> 00:00:46.086
Once a proud talk-show host. he has
been driven by a changing ecosystem...

9
00:00:46.170 --> 00:00:51.550
