meagerest of morsels...

13
00:01:09.230 --> 00:01:11.780
the random call-in fan.

14
00:01:11.860 --> 00:01:17.240
Unhinged by the feral scent
of their mild enthusiasm...

15
00:01:17.320 --> 00:01:21.200
